sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant SRV  as 2030.5 Server
    participant C    as C Binary
    participant PY   as Python Bridge
    participant MB   as Modbus Device

    Note over SRV,C: server has DefaultDERControl configured<br/>(applies when no active event)

    SRV ->> C: DefaultDERControl {DERControlBase: baseline setpoints}

    C   ->> PY: EVENT_JSON: {type:default_control,<br/>control:{opModMaxLimW:10000, opModConnect:true}}

    PY  ->> PY: bridge.apply(event), _active_registers.clear()
    PY  ->> MB: write_register(40100, 10000)  # max_lim_w
    MB  -->> PY: ok
    PY  ->> MB: write_register(40104, 1)      # connect
    MB  -->> PY: ok

    Note over PY: _active_registers = {40100:10000, 40104:1}
    Note over PY: stays active until superseded by higher-priority event
